WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script5 — Hmoob

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Nyob zoo!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:06.059
Koj vừa tau txais koj lub cuab yeej tshiab ntawm peb lub chaw kho mob, Ortho Espace 3D.

3
00:00:06.059 --> 00:00:09.439
Cov hnub thawj yog lub sijhawm tseem ceeb ntawm kev hloov.

4
00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:12.034
Nov yog peb cov lus qhia kom pib tau zoo.

5
00:00:13.434 --> 00:00:15.058
Kev tso rau.

6
00:00:15.008 --> 00:00:18.451
Ua ntej hnav ib tais mis los yog thoom nyias tsis muaj kev xaws tuab.

7
00:00:18.451 --> 00:00:22.709
Ces tso lub cuab yeej raws li cov cim kws kho mob qhia.

8
00:00:22.709 --> 00:00:25.889
Kaw cov hlua txuas los qis mus rau saud, tsis txhob kaw nruj dhau.

9
00:00:27.289 --> 00:00:29.178
Kev nce sijhawm hnav.

10
00:00:29.128 --> 00:00:32.115
Cov hnub thawj, txwv kev hnav rau ob teev.

11
00:00:32.115 --> 00:00:35.064
Nce zuj zus raws li koj kev zam tau.

12
00:00:35.064 --> 00:00:39.435
Yog koj xav tsis zoo los yog mob, tshem lub cuab yeej tawm thiab hu rau peb.

13
00:00:40.835 --> 00:00:42.526
Koj tawv nqaij li xwm txheej.

14
00:00:42.476 --> 00:00:46.756
Tom qab txhua zaug hnav, xyuas tawv nqaij uas kov lub cuab yeej.

15
00:00:46.756 --> 00:00:50.036
Liab me ntsis uas ploj hauv nees nkaum feeb yog ib qho ib txwm muaj.

16
00:00:50.036 --> 00:00:54.803
Tab sis liab txuas ntxiv los yog qhov raug xav tau kev ntsib kws kho mob sai sai.

17
00:00:56.203 --> 00:00:58.007
Kev siv txhua hnub.

18
00:00:57.957 --> 00:01:02.936
Hnav koj lub cuab yeej rau txhua yam hauj lwm ib txwm ua, nce zuj zus kev siv zog.

19
00:01:02.936 --> 00:01:08.031
Kev kho mob rau lub cev yuav pab koj rov qab tau kev ywj siab thiab kev zoo ib txwm hauv txhua yam.

20
00:01:09.431 --> 00:01:12.739
Peb pab neeg nyob kom teb koj cov lus nug.

21
00:01:12.689 --> 00:01:16.441
Tsis txhob ua siab ntsws hu rau peb los yog xa lus hauv WhatsApp.

22
00:01:16.441 --> 00:01:18.717
Sib zog, nej tsis nyob ib leeg!
